[src:manova/hotelling-s-t-squared-distribution] Then, use the quantity on the left hand side to evaluate the *p*-value corresponding to the sample, which comes from the *F*-distribution.
[src:manova/hotelling-s-t-squared-distribution] A confidence region may also be determined using similar logic.
